# Integration test (cross-participant): Alice on participant1 issues an Asset
# owned by Bob, whose party is hosted on participant2. We submit via Alice's
# participant (%ledger) and trace the SAME committed update from Bob's separate
# participant (%ledger2) -- proving the contract is visible across participants
# on the shared synchronizer. Run the suite with --parties Alice@1,Bob@2.
#
# RUN: ID=$(%dpm submit --submitter %ledger --act-as %alice --template '#asset-tests:Asset:Asset' --arg issuer=%alice --arg owner=%bob --arg name=SILVER --arg quantity=50) \
# RUN:   && %dpm trace "$ID" --submitter %ledger2 --read-as %bob --wait 30 --color never | FileCheck %s

# CHECK: Canton trace
# CHECK: CREATE Asset:Asset
# CHECK: signatories: Alice
# CHECK: name: SILVER{{.*}}quantity: 50
